Philosophy

Redefining
Normality

We've created M-EM01 for the dawn of a new generation. Empathic yet reserved, undefined by societal traditions, these individuals simultaneously exist between physical and digital realms.

We exist beyond the binary. We do not align with societal conventions. M-EM01 strives to redefine what is deemed 'normal' by uplifting unique personalities in a new world no longer shaped by pre-judgment.

alien
inside you

page 0008

Sustainability

Green

An environmentally conscious design that retains product quality is core to our ethos. Our eco-friendly toothbrush features bio-based ergonomic bristles.

We fabricate from a non-GMO, biodegradable, plant-based blend with bio-based filaments from castor oil. Fully-biodegradable vacuum pouches with 100% recycled cardboard labels.

Non-GMO Biodegradable Plant-Based Eco-Friendly
